# Contributing

WYRIWYD was developed as a hackday demo.
There is plenty of scope for further development and contributions are welcome.

- Please use the Issue Tracker for bug reports and feature proposals.
- Contributions can be made by forking on Github and
  [making a pull request](https://help.github.com/en/articles/creating-a-pull-request-from-a-fork).
  Before beginning ambitious changes, please discuss your ideas with
  the owners of this repository through the Issue tracker.
- Please bear in mind that this package is intended for novice
  programmers; avoid introducing large/complex dependencies or a
  requirement for advanced framework knowlege.